<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <style>
    @font-face {
  font-family: Avenir-next;
  src: url("fonts/avenir next sv/AvenirNextLTPro-Regular.otf") format("opentype");
}

body{
  font-family: Avenir-next;
}

.flex-container, .flex-container-body, #flex-button,
.flex-center, #flex-body, .container-images,
.container {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
}

.container-head-image-left {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
}

.container-head-image-right {
  padding: 1em 0 1em 0;
}

#text-title {
  color: #666;
  font-size: 20px;
}

#text-body {
  color:  grey;
  text-align: center;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  line-height: 25px;
  font-weight: 600;
}

#link-google {
  color: #8D7AFF;
}

.btn-register {
  font-weight: bold;
  border-radius: 3px;
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 16px;
  color: #8D7AFF;
  text-decoration: none;
  border-color: #8D7AFF;
  border-width: 1px;
  border-style: solid;
  padding: .7em 1em .7em 1em;
  width: 50%;
}

#flex-button {
  padding: 1em;
}

#text-rent-homie {
  font-weight: bold;
  color:  grey;
}

.text-footer {
  font-weight: bold;
  color:  grey;
  font-size: 16px;
  text-align: center;
  padding-top: 1.5em;
}

img {
  display: block;
  margin: auto;
}

.img-bottom {
  width: 150px;
}

.container-images-columns {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  flex-direction: column;
}

.responsive-image {
  max-width: 100%;
}

.cell img {
  display: block;
  padding: 0em 2em;
}

@media screen and (min-width: 600px) {
  .grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    flex-direction: row;
  }

  .cell {
    width: 50%;
  }
}

@media screen and (min-width: 1000px) {
  .cell {
    width: calc(100% / 3);
  }
}

.cell {
  margin: 1rem;
}

@media screen and (min-width: 600px) {
  .cell {
    width: calc(50% - 2rem);
  }
}

@media screen and (min-width: 1000px) {
  .cell {
    width: calc(33.3333% - 2rem);
  }
}
    </style>
    <title>Registro</title>
  </head>
  <body>

    <div class="flex-container">
      <div class="flex-container-head">
        <div class="container-head-image-left">
          <%= image_tag 'homie', class: "image-head" %>
        </div>
        <div class="container-head-image-right">
          <%= image_tag 'ribbon', class: "image-head" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex-container-body">
      <div class="flexbox-container">
        <div class="container-images-columns">

          <div class="flex-center">
              <p id="text-title">Hola Propietario Apellido,</p>
          </div>
          
          <p id="text-body">
            <span>Has iniciado un registro para publicar tu propiedad en nuestra plataforma,</span>
            <span><a id="link-google" href="https://www.google.com.mx" target="_black">los espacios y amenidades</a> son algunos extras que ayudan</span> 
            <span>a que tu propiedad se rente mas rapido, especificalos ahora.</span>
          </p>

          <div id="flex-button">
            <a class="btn-register" href="#" >Continuar registro</a>
          </div>

          <div class="flex-center">
              <p id="text-rent-homie">Rentar en Homie tiene varios beneficios: </p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="cell">
          <img src="images/investigacion.png" alt="" width="150" >
          <p class="text-footer">Obtén al mejor inquilino</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cell">
          <img src="images/apartado.png" alt="" width="150" >
          <p class="text-footer">Garantía de pago puntual</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cell">
          <img src="images/firma.png" alt="" width="150" >
          <p class="text-footer">Protección jurídica</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </body>
</html>